alerts.message: Insufficient hip rotation in 38.8% of strokes
Excessive knee flexion in 76.5% of frames

recommendations.title: Improve Power Generation
recommendations.description: Using arm-only swings increases injury risk and reduces power.
actions: Focus on hip rotation before arm swing
Watch tutorial videos on kinetic chain

recommendations.title: Protect Your Knees
recommendations.description: Deep squatting increases patellar tendinitis risk.
actions: Consider knee support if pain persists

recommendations.title: Elbow Positioning
recommendations.description: Elbow angles outside optimal range detected.
actions: Focus on proper elbow extension for each stroke
Practice with lighter paddle if experiencing pain
